,{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notifyPropertiesChange","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"()","kind":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/notifypropertieschange()","title":"notifyPropertiesChange()","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Notifies that properties have changed by incrementing the update counter.","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"notifyPropertiesChange","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/notifyPropertiesChange()"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk","type":"topic","title":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Version: 8.0.3"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","abstract":[{"text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"value":"occ","op":"replace","path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage"},{"value":"Instance Method","op":"replace","path":"\/metadata\/roleHeading"},{"value":"notifyPropertiesChange","op":"replace","path":"\/metadata\/title"},{"value":"method","op":"replace","path":"\/metadata\/symbolKind"},{"value":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notifyPropertiesChange"}],"op":"replace","path":"\/metadata\/fragments"},{"value":null,"op":"add","path":"\/topicSections"},{"value":null,"op":"add","path":"\/relationshipsSections"},{"value":null,"op":"add","path":"\/seeAlsoSections"},{"value":{"declarations":[{"tokens":[